              <description>传输错误中断使能。注意：此位由软件置位和清零。通道使能（EN = 1）时不得写入此位。通道使能（EN = 1）时此位并非只读。</description>
              <bitOffset>3</bitOffset>
              <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
              <access>read-write</access>
              <enumeratedValues>
                <enumeratedValue>
